《'''Shine a Light'''》是[[韓國|韓國]][[男子音樂組合|男子音樂組合]][[BIGBANG|BIGBANG]]隊長[[G-Dragon|G-Dragon]]在發行第一張正規專輯《{{link-en|Heartbreaker (G-Dragon專輯)|Heartbreaker (G-Dragon album)|Heartbreaker}}》後舉行為期兩天的首次個人演唱會。

==爭議==
演唱會結束後隨即因表演內容過於情色、暴力，不適合未成年人士觀看而引發爭議<ref>{{cite web| title = Singer G-Dragon Faces Obscenity Probe| author = | publisher = The Chosunilbo| date = 2009-12-11| url = http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2009/12/11/2009121100740.html| accessdate = 2009-12-27| archive-date = 2010-01-05| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100105100437/http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2009/12/11/2009121100740.html| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| title = G-Dragon's Suggestive Concert Creates Stir| author = Cho, Jae-hyon| publisher = The Korean Times| date = 2009-12-08| url = http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/art/2010/01/135_56865.html| accessdate = 2009-12-27| archive-date = 2012-09-11| archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6AasU9mtk?url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/art/2010/01/135_56865.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>，甚至因事件越演越烈遭到[[大韓民國保健福祉部|大韓民國保健福祉部]]要求政府檢察官針對G-Dragon及所屬經紀公司[[YG娛樂|YG娛樂]]在演唱會表演的爭議性內容以涉嫌違反「青少年保護法」進行調查<ref>{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120916114235/http://www.mb.com.ph/articles/234746/fans-defend-gdragon-against-concert-controversy|url=http://www.mb.com.ph/articles/234746/fans-defend-gdragon-against-concert-controversy|title=Fans defend G-Dragon against concert controversy|archivedate=2012-09-16|language=en|accessdate=2017-04-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=G-Dragon fans file petition over concert fiasco |author=Hicap, Jonathan M. |publisher=The Manila Publishing Corporation |date=2010-01-08 |url=http://www.mb.com.ph/node/237468/gdragon-fan |accessdate=2010-01-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100206084443/http://www.mb.com.ph/node/237468/gdragon-fan |archivedate=2010-02-06 }}</ref>。此次案件在2010年3月15日審結，法院以「雖然他（G-Dragon）的作品像〈Korean Dream〉等已被定為對青少年有害，但並不代表其演唱會亦不適合青少年欣賞；加上演唱歌曲〈Breathe〉時在床上與女舞蹈員的動作亦未到淫穢地步。」宣佈G-Dragon罪名不成立<ref>{{cite web| title = '선정성 재판' G드래곤 콘서트, 영화도 12세可| author = Lee, Jae-hoon| publisher = Nate.com| date = 2010-04-15| url = http://news.nate.com/view/20100415n20586| accessdate = 2010-01-15| language = ko| archive-date = 2012-09-11| archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6AasaEBN6?url=http://news.nate.com/view/20100415n20586| dead-url = no}}</ref>，但法庭指演唱會主辦單位YG娛樂違反公演法而被判300萬韓圜罰金（約新臺幣8萬5千元）。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://kpopn.niusnews.com/=K0h112 |title=G-Dragon 過度性感的演唱會官司繼續 |language=中文 |publisher=韓娛最前線 |date=2010-04-12 |accessdate=2016-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223140408/http://kpopn.niusnews.com/=K0h112 |archive-date=2016-12-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

